== NO MIGRATIONS NEEDED ==
No new database migrations were required. The existing schema already had all necessary columns:
- jobs.sentinel_reached (BOOLEAN)
- jobs.output (TEXT)
- sessions.params (JSONB) - stores sentinel value

== SUMMARY ==
Feature 18 (Loop Workflows) was mostly already implemented by previous tasks. The key addition was:
1. Server-side double-check of sentinel in the output field (not just trusting the worker's sentinel_reached flag)
2. Comprehensive integration tests covering all spec requirements including edge cases (case sensitivity, substring matching, multi-iteration, failure handling)
